
## When negotiating salary use these five powerful phrases.

1. I have thoroughly researched the market and average salary for someone of my skill set and experiences is in range of (salary).

2. Considering my qualifications and the responsibilites of the role .I was hoping we could discuss the salary in the ball park of.

3. I am enthusiastic about joining the team and I believe that contributions would align well with the salary in the range of.

4. I bring valuable skill and expertise to this role and i was wondering if there was room for negotiation on the salary.
